(6, 1, 'blogs', 'new_blog_post', '<a href="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/members/atropos/" title="Atropos">Atropos</a> wrote a new post, <a href="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/2013/07/tamriel-foundry-development-faq/">Tamriel Foundry Development FAQ</a>', 'Quisque justo dui, tempor interdum arcu non, ornare faucibus mauris. Class aptent taciti sociosqu ad litora torquent per conubia nostra, per inceptos himenaeos. Vivamus et magna sit amet nulla posuere tincidunt [&hellip;]', 'http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/2013/07/tamriel-foundry-development-faq/', 1, 38, '2013-08-04 04:40:29', 0, 0, 0, 0),
