(8, 1, 'blogs', 'new_blog_post', '<a href="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/members/atropos/" title="Atropos">Atropos</a> wrote a new post, <a href="http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/2013/08/tf-theme-update/">Tamriel Foundry Theme Updated</a>', 'Praesent justo sem, venenatis non nulla ac, malesuada cursus elit. Pellentesque consequat placerat augue in condimentum. Curabitur quis felis sit amet leo condimentum viverra vitae sed tortor. Proin volutpat risus [&hellip;]', 'http://localhost/tamrielfoundry/2013/08/tf-theme-update/', 1, 42, '2013-08-04 04:42:28', 0, 0, 0, 0),
